  icon: {fileID: 2800000, guid: 727a75301c3d24613a3ebcec4a24c2c8, type: 3}
  title: ARChess
  sections:
  - heading: Project overview
    text: ARChess is a Unity 6 chess client with local PvP, LAN play, server-backed AI moves, live coaching, post-game review, and Android AR mode.
    linkText:
    url:
  - heading: Important scenes
    text: Start from Assets/Scenes/MainMenu.unity. ChessScene.unity contains the persistent game manager, 2D board canvas, HUD, timers, promotion UI, and game-over UI.
    linkText:
    url:
  - heading: Source folders
    text: Game code lives under Assets/Sources. The current AI service lives under server. The local_server folder is an older FastAPI prototype kept for reference.
    linkText:
    url:
  - heading: Documentation
    text: See README.md and docs for architecture, class diagrams, LAN sequences, scene hierarchy, color theme, setup, and test notes.
    linkText: Open README
    url: README.md
  loadedLayout: 1
